OL,5, Over 50 authors have called on the     
OL,6, Edinburgh International Book festival  
OL,7, to cut ties with one of its sponsors   
OL,8, over climate concerns.                 
OL,10,FA joint letter urges organisers to put 
OL,11,Fpressure on Baillie Gifford over its   
OL,12,Finvestment in fossil fuels.            
OL,14,FThe festival director later called for 
OL,15,Fan "open discussion" about the issue   
OL,16,Fduring the event, which starts on      
OL,17,FSaturday.                              
OL,19,FBaillie Gifford has said it is not a   
OL,20,Fsignificant investor in the sector.    
